        "id": "comment-intro",
        "parent_id": null,
        "type": "nodetool.workflows.base_node.Comment",
        "data": {
          "comment": "# 🔀 Conditional Logic Engine\n\nRoute a number through compare, boolean, and switch nodes to demonstrate multi-branch decision logic, then assemble a report.\n\n**Pipeline:** Number → compare (>100, <50) → OR → conditional switches → report\n\n**Try this:** change the input value (0–100) and watch which branch fires."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "selected": false,
          "position": {
            "x": 0,
            "y": -220
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 460,
          "height": 180,
          "selectable": true
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {},
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "2",
        "type": "nodetool.text.Prompt",
        "data": {
          "prompt": "## Conditional Logic Decision Result\n\n**Input Value:** {{ value }}\n\n**Condition Checks:**\n- Greater than 100? {{ gt_100 }}\n- Less than 50? {{ lt_50 }}\n- Combined (OR): {{ combined }}\n- Route Decision: {{ route }}\n\n**Processing Path:**\n{{ processing }}\n\n**Decision Logic:**\nThis workflow demonstrates:\n- Multiple condition evaluation\n- Logical operations (OR gate)\n- Conditional branching\n- Multi-path routing\n- Result aggregation"
        },
        "ui_properties": {
